eng: AMISYN Literature of Amikacin Sulfate 10% Injectable Generic name: Amikacin Sulfate 10% injectable Brand name: Amisyn English name: Amikacin Sulfate 10% injectable BRI ST it: Amikacin 10% w/v Chinese name: Acti ingredi Chemical nam 6-0-(3-Amino-3-deoxy-a-D-glucopyranosyl)-4-O-(6-Amino-6- deoxy-a-D-glucopyranosyl)-N- (4-amino-2-hydroxybutyry-2-deoxystreptamine)Sulfate 0 OH S04 Q oH o OH HN NH; CuHN:Op 1.8 HyS0, 76215 CnHoNOy- 2H,S0; 78176 Physical property: Amisyn is a yellow clear sterile liquid Pharmacology: Amikacin is a semi-synthetic aminoglycoside antibiotic derived from Kanamycin. Amikacin is taken up into sensitive bacterial cells by an active transport process which is inhibited in anaerobic, acidic, or hyperosmolar environments. Within the cells they bind to the 30S and to some extent to the 503, subunits of the bacterial ribosome, inhibiting protein synthesis and ‘generating errors in the transeription of the genetic codes. Indi tion: Amikacin has bactericidal action against Escherichia, Brucella, Calymmatobacterium, Citrobacter, Enterobacter, Francisella, Klebsiella, Proteus, Salmonella, Pasteurella, Pseudomonas, Staphylococeus, Listeria, Actinomycetes, Mycoplasmas, Mycobacterium. Amisyn is specially indicated when animals are under severe Gram-negative and other infections and when such infections are resistant to other Aminoglycosides. Administration and Dosage Use intra-muscular injection For horse, cattle, swine, poultry:0.05ml to 0.1ml per Kg body weight, twice daily for 2 to 3 days Adverse effects Prolonged and overdose may cause ofotoxicity, nephrotoxicity, loss of appetite, rashes, hypersensitivity, and neuro-muscular blocking effects. Precautions 1. Amikacin is inactivated in vitro by various penicillins and cephalosporins via an interaction with the beta-lactam ring. Avoid concurrent usage. 2. Due to the lack of effective antidote, if toxicity ocours, replenish large amount of water. 3. Do not administer intravenously. This may cause respiratory depression. 4. To prevent nephrotoxicity, it is important for animals to have high water intake during treatment Withdrawal:28 days Standard:100m1:10g, Packing: 10mV/ampoule SOml/vial 100ml/vial StorageLStore Amisyn in sealed containers and in a cool and dry place.
